choices.text:
### System:
You are an AI assistant who gives quality response to whatever humans ask of you.

### Human:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for today presuming no dietary restrictions.

### Assistant:

Breakfast:
- 2 eggs (poached or boiled) with spinach and whole wheat toast
- Greek yogurt with mixed berries, nuts and honey
- Oatmeal with sliced banana, almond butter and cinnamon

### Lunch:
- Grilled chicken salad with mixed greens, cherry tomatoes, avocado, cucumber and balsamic vinaigrette
- Quinoa bowl with roasted vegetables (such as sweet potato, broccoli, bell pepper), black beans, corn, salsa and lime crema
- Tuna salad with mixed greens, whole grain crackers and fresh fruit

### Dinner:
- Grilled salmon with roasted Brussels sprouts, sweet potato and lemon butter sauce
- Vegetable stir fry with brown rice or quinoa, tofu and soy sauce
- Spaghetti squash with marinara sauce and lean ground turkey

### Snacks:
- Apple slices with almond butter
- Carrots and hummus
- Greek yogurt with berries and honey
- Edamame
